OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBrexit: Imperial units only
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpart of laws revamp, says  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FNo 10                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government says its review of EU   
OL,6, rules on imperial measures for traders 
OL,7, is only a "small part" of plans to     
OL,8, reshape laws after Brexit.             
OL,10,FThe overhaul could permit retailers to 
OL,11,Fonce again sell goods only using       
OL,12,FBritain's traditional weighing system. 
OL,14,FLabour's deputy leader Angela Rayner   
OL,15,Fhas said it shows ministers are "out of
OL,16,Ftouch" with voters' priorities.        
OL,18,FBut No 10 said it was just one element 
OL,19,Fof its drive to recast laws inherited  
OL,20,Ffrom the EU.                           
